        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Before integration, ensure your environment meets the prerequisites: Python 3.8+, access to the Qwen API endpoint, and valid authentication tokens. Install the client library via "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "pip install qwen-image-edit-client",
            "code": true
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ". Initialize the client with your API key and set the model to "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "QwenImageEdit_Plus_NF4",
            "code": true
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ". Basic usage involves sending an image URL and specifying edit parameters, such as "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "edit_type",
            "code": true
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " and "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "output_format",
            "code": true
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ". Test with a simple request to verify connectivity and response handling."
          }
