            "text": "Extend functionality with multi-step edits. Chain API calls by using the output of one edit as input to another, such as applying 'enhance' followed by 'resize'. Implement custom preprocessing, like image normalization, before sending to the API. For real-time applications, use WebSockets for streaming edits on video frames. Example code snippet for a chained edit:"
